and pour wine.

21:15.191 --> 21:17.692
Polly? Focus for one second, okay?

21:20.780 --> 21:23.323
So, hey, I got to go circulate.

21:25.660 --> 21:28.453
So, Sandy, you're good though?
You're still acting?

21:28.537 --> 21:31.206
I am.
Yeah, it's going incredibly well.

21:31.499 --> 21:34.960
I'm actually headlining a new
revival of Jesus Christ Superstar.

21:35.044 --> 21:36.544
That's great!

21:36.629 --> 21:39.214
- It was really good seeing you guys.
- You, too.

21:39.340 --> 21:41.299
- See you!
- All right. Bye, Polly.

21:41.384 --> 21:42.717
Be good.

21:42.843 --> 21:43.969
More wine?

21:44.470 --> 21:47.889
Polly Prince. It's funny, huh?
Seeing her.

21:48.849 --> 21:50.976
- Are you okay?
- Great, thank you.

21:53.896 --> 21:55.480
She looks good.

21:56.315 --> 21:56.481
Let it rain!

21:56.482 --> 21:57.732
Let it rain!

21:59.485 --> 22:01.236
