with you, Sasquatch.

22:31.767 --> 22:33.351
Let's get it on.

22:34.395 --> 22:37.939
Pick and roll! Take it rough!
Outlet!

22:38.441 --> 22:39.899
Rain dance!

22:40.443 --> 22:41.860
Sandy, come on.

22:44.071 --> 22:45.363
I got him.

22:46.282 --> 22:47.782
White Chocolate!

22:48.951 --> 22:50.285
Raindrops!

22:51.620 --> 22:53.121
Old school!

22:54.790 --> 22:56.791
T. Time-out.

22:56.876 --> 22:59.252
I'm burning. My lungs are burning.

22:59.795 --> 23:01.463
Time-out.

23:01.797 --> 23:04.382
So why do you think
Polly's so wrong for me?

23:05.718 --> 23:07.635
You don't even know this girl.

23:07.762 --> 23:10.055
You haven't seen her
since seventh grade.

23:10.139 --> 23:11.389
How different could she be?

23:11.474 --> 23:13.475
