how to cover this man right here.

24:09.865 --> 24:11.199
Let's play.

24:35.391 --> 24:39.727
Can I get the number for a Polly
Prince, please? Prince with a "P."

24:42.898 --> 24:45.400
Okay, great.
Can I get the address as well?

24:58.622 --> 24:59.706
Hello.

25:07.715 --> 25:09.048
Oh, shit!

25:10.759 --> 25:12.719
- Hi. This is Reuben.
- No!

25:12.803 --> 25:15.013
I'm unable to get to the phone
right now

25:15.097 --> 25:17.473
but please leave a detailed message
after the beep.

25:17.600 --> 25:19.934
If you're calling for Lisa...

26:12.196 --> 26:14.197
Gladys, I got to call you back.

26:18.285 --> 26:20.870
