26:36.512 --> 26:39.764
Because I got a hang-up
so I did that star-69 thingy.

26:39.848 --> 26:43.017
And I swore
I got your answering machine.

26:43.978 --> 26:46.062
Really? I heard that
from a few people,

26:46.188 --> 26:48.815
so maybe the phone lines
got crossed or something.

26:48.899 --> 26:51.859
- You doing some shopping?
- Oh, yeah.

26:52.361 --> 26:55.697
Gosh, I spent like $200
on this loofah.

26:56.365 --> 26:59.701
It's supposed to be specially made
in Sweden or something.

26:59.827 --> 27:00.868
Wow.

27:01.870 --> 27:04.247
Would you like to go
to dinner sometime?

27:05.207 --> 27:08.876
Oh, yeah. Okay.
You know, I'm not sure.

27:09.712 --> 27:11.212
Okay. Really?

27:11.338 --> 27:13.923
