to catch up on stuff and all that.

27:16.719 --> 27:19.220
I just got to check my schedule.

27:19.346 --> 27:22.098
All right, how about
I give you my card?

27:22.224 --> 27:23.683
Here you go.

27:24.560 --> 27:27.228
On the back I've written
my home and my cell number.

27:27.354 --> 27:29.230
- There's also a fax number.
- Right on.

27:29.356 --> 27:31.024
And a pager number, too.

27:31.108 --> 27:33.901
"Reuben Feffer,
Senior Risk Assessment Analysist."

27:34.028 --> 27:35.945
- Right. Analyst.
- Analyst.

27:36.780 --> 27:38.281
Right.

27:38.949 --> 27:40.450
All right.

27:42.411 --> 27:43.911
See you.

27:48.584 --> 27:50.376
- See you.
- See you later.

27:57.468 --> 27:59.302
Leland Van Lew's office.
This is Deborah.

27:59.428 --> 28:02.972
Reuben Feffer from Indursky & Sons
calling for Mr. Van Lew.

28:03.098 --> 28:06.642
Right. The insurance man.
He's in the hospital.

28:06.727 --> 28:09.187
He got bit swimming
with great whites.

28:09.271 --> 28:11.230
- Swimming with who?
- Great white sharks.

28:11.315 --> 28:13.107
But don't worry.
It was only a flesh wound.

28:16.612 --> 28:18.780
He's due in Los Angeles
next week.

28:18.906 --> 28:22.033
- Should I set something up for then?
- Could you hang on, please?

28:22.117 --> 28:23.618
No worries.

28:23.952 --> 28:27.163
- Hi, Reuben. It's Polly Prince.
- Hey, Polly.

28:28.248 --> 28:29.248
How's it going?

28:29.333 --> 28:30.958
