28:48.602 --> 28:52.438
No, I'm actually not sure.
I'll talk to you later. Bye!

28:52.523 --> 28:53.940
Okay, hello?

28:55.150 --> 28:57.276
One, two, three, and...

28:57.361 --> 28:59.404
