since you were last single.

30:45.928 --> 30:47.261
Now listen...

30:48.096 --> 30:50.890
when I'm making out with a girl
for the first time,

30:50.974 --> 30:53.267
I like to give her
a little spanking.

30:53.477 --> 30:55.061
- What?
- Nothing violent.

30:55.145 --> 30:58.022
Just tap her real light
on the tush and say,

30:58.106 --> 31:01.275
"Hey, I'm your daddy."

31:01.985 --> 31:03.486
Listen to me.

31:04.071 --> 31:06.531
- What are you doing?
- I'm blotting the grease.

31:06.615 --> 31:10.284
