or something, you know?

31:27.302 --> 31:31.138
I actually think it's not gonna
work out, but I'm pulling for you.

31:32.140 --> 31:34.850
Just pray to God
she doesn't go ethnic.

31:35.310 --> 31:38.145
- The place didn't sound ethnic.
- What was the name?

31:38.230 --> 31:39.397
Al Hafez.

31:43.485 --> 31:46.904
- So, when did you live in Morocco?
- In the late '90s.

31:46.989 --> 31:50.032
I bounced around to a bunch
of places over the past few years.

31:50.158 --> 31:51.993
- Like where?
- Oh, God, where?

31:52.077 --> 31:56.706
Let's see, Austin, Istanbul,
Sri Lanka, Portland,

31:56.832 --> 31:59.250
Costa Rica, Buffalo,
a couple other places.

31:59.334 --> 32:02.587
- Wow. Were you in the Peace Corps?
- No, I just like to move a lot.

32:02.671 --> 32:05.756
I get stir-crazy if I'm stuck
in one place too long, you know?

32:05.841 --> 32:07.258
Yeah, completely.

32:08.385 --> 32:09.885
Remember,
you were the person who...

32:09.970 --> 32:11.178
Oh, my God!

32:11.263 --> 32:13.681
I can't believe you remember that.

32:13.765 --> 32:17.435
Of course! You were the greatest
delegate in Model UN history.

32:17.519 --> 32:20.688
I guess I did manage
to pass a few resolutions.

32:22.065 --> 32:25.651
Are you okay? Because you're
sweating pretty profusely.

32:25.736 --> 32:29.030
No, I'm fine. I always react
this way to spicy food.

32:29.615 --> 32:30.740
But I love it.

32:30.866 --> 32:33.034
