like an old young guy.

32:39.958 --> 32:41.208
Well, it just hasn't happened.

32:42.419 --> 32:44.962
But what about you?
You ever gotten close?

32:45.047 --> 32:49.258
To the whole marriage thing?
Oh, God, no. No way, no. No.

32:50.385 --> 32:53.971
I'm not really big on the whole
long-term commitment thing.

32:54.973 --> 32:57.266
Why, are you coming
out of a bad relationship?

32:57.392 --> 32:59.769
No. I'm coming
out of eight bad relationships.

32:59.895 --> 33:00.936
Eight?

33:01.063 --> 33:04.398
- You sure I can't get you a towel?
- No, I'm good.

33:04.483 --> 33:08.402
But if the right person came along,
things might be different, right?

33:08.737 --> 33:11.739
Yeah. You're probably right.

33:14.284 --> 33:15.493
Sorry.

33:17.913 --> 33:20.539
- You mind if I go to the men's room?
- Please, sure.

33:20.624 --> 33:21.666
Oh, gosh!

33:24.461 --> 33:27.672
Occupied. I'm going to be here
all night, dude.

33:31.426 --> 33:33.719
- All right, well, this is me.
- Great.

33:33.804 --> 33:35.262
Why don't you come upstairs

33:35.347 --> 33:37.306
and I'll make you
some coffee or tea.

33:37.432 --> 33:38.557
Great.

33:38.642 --> 33:41.060
I just got to find my keys here.

33:41.144 --> 33:42.520
Oh, shoot.

33:46.024 --> 33:47.775
Right there, I hear them.

33:50.821 --> 33:52.530
Oh, yeah. Okay.

33:52.614 --> 33:53.489
- Wow! This is great, so cozy.
- Thanks.

33:53.490 --> 33:55.908
- Wow! This is great, so cozy.
- Thanks.

33:55.992 --> 33:59.620
- Did you just move in?
- No, I've been here four months.

34:00.288 --> 34:01.914
Rat! Rat in the house!

34:01.998 --> 34:06.043
Oh, no. This is Rodolfo.
He's a ferret.

34:06.461 --> 34:08.879
I got him in Sicily
at a flea market years ago.

34:08.964 --> 34:11.297
He's old.
He can't really see anymore.

34:12.134 --> 34:14.635
