and serve you for all of eternity.

35:57.489 --> 36:00.783
I'll adopt a Somalian kid
or I'll work in Calcutta

36:00.909 --> 36:04.328
or I'll just...
Please, make the water go down.

36:18.009 --> 36:19.510
Oh, my God!

36:22.013 --> 36:23.931
- This was fun.
- Yes.

36:25.183 --> 36:27.810
If I'd known your grandmother
embroidered that towel,

36:27.936 --> 36:30.521
- I would've never...
- Really, that's okay.

36:31.147 --> 36:35.109
- Okay, well, good night, Polly.
- Good night, Reuben.

36:35.777 --> 36:37.194
- Good night.
- Okay.

36:37.279 --> 36:39.530
- All right, okay.
- All right, that's nice.

36:46.121 --> 36:48.664
Why would you make
number two in her apartment?

36:48.790 --> 36:51.458
She asked me to come upstairs.
What should I have done?

36:51.543 --> 36:54.211
Tell her you're tired
and shag ass out of there.

36:54.296 --> 36:55.337
Guys.

36:56.214 --> 36:58.382
- What was that?
- I called her to apologize.

36:58.466 --> 37:02.177
It doesn't matter, because I doubt
she'll ever want to see me again.

37:02.304 --> 37:04.388
- I got to call you back.
- Cool.

37:04.472 --> 37:05.639
Mr. Van Lew?

37:06.850 --> 37:09.393
- Feffer?
- Yes. Hi, Reuben Feffer.

37:09.477 --> 37:11.437
I recognized you
from the Forbes cover.

37:11.521 --> 37:14.440
You're way early, sport.
Come on, then. Get in.

37:14.524 --> 37:16.817
- Is this the service elevator?
- Yeah.

37:17.319 --> 37:20.362
I don't think we'll have a problem
with this insurance business.

37:20.488 --> 37:23.574
Sure, I take chances, but you can't
build a successful business

37:23.658 --> 37:25.492
- without the occasional risk.
- Of course.

37:25.577 --> 37:29.079
What I'm trying to determine are the
kinds of risks you actually take.

37:29.164 --> 37:30.539
Only the calculated ones.

37:30.624 --> 37:32.708
Trust me, I plan on being around
for ages.

37:33.001 --> 37:36.337
I know we'd really love to give you
a policy if we can make it work.

37:36.421 --> 37:38.672
- We'll make it work, sport.
- Great.

37:39.341 --> 37:42.801
- So, what are we doing on the roof?
- I'm doing a bit of a BASE jump.

37:42.886 --> 37:46.013
