all right?

37:56.733 --> 38:00.861
- Hey, Reuben, it's Polly Prince.
- Polly, how's it going?

38:00.946 --> 38:04.239
- I'll shout when I'm through, okay?
- No, that's not all right.

38:04.324 --> 38:05.407
Can I call you back?

38:05.492 --> 38:08.077
I just wanted to tell you
I got your message.

38:08.161 --> 38:11.246
Let's just start over
and forget about the loofah thing.

38:11.331 --> 38:12.665
Holy shit! No!

38:14.417 --> 38:15.459
Holy shit!

38:15.543 --> 38:17.169
