38:17.754 --> 38:20.255
Relax. Leland's meeting
with the insurance guy right now.

38:20.340 --> 38:22.758
Whoa! Yeah!

38:27.180 --> 38:28.514
Oh, crap!

38:28.640 --> 38:31.225
- Oh, shit!
- I'll call you in the next few days.

38:31.309 --> 38:33.852
Leland to Feffer. You there, mate?

38:34.312 --> 38:36.397
Yes, Feffer to Leland, hello?

38:36.481 --> 38:37.982
Come on down and give us a hand.

38:38.066 --> 38:40.067
