who I ran into yesterday.

40:04.486 --> 40:06.111
- Who's that?
- Lisa's mother.

40:06.196 --> 40:07.279
Mmm-hmm. That's good.

40:07.363 --> 40:09.698
Dad, did you try this...
What's this called?

40:09.783 --> 40:11.742
- Saag.
- Saag. Did you try this?

40:11.826 --> 40:15.537
