42:00.435 --> 42:02.019
Or not. I mean, either way.

42:02.103 --> 42:05.606
Oh, if you do come,
you should wear comfortable shoes.

42:05.690 --> 42:08.483
That is, if you come,
which you totally don't have to.

42:08.568 --> 42:10.777
