42:35.303 --> 42:38.013
It's the best underground
salsa club in New York.

42:38.097 --> 42:42.017
- I'm not really a big dancer.
- It's easier than it looks.

42:43.770 --> 42:46.730
- There you go. Feel it in your legs.
- All right.

42:47.232 --> 42:48.315
Sorry.

42:48.399 --> 42:51.610
