a little less than that.

43:00.370 --> 43:01.828
Work it!

43:05.875 --> 43:09.378
- Looking good, Pollyanna.
- Hey, Javi.

43:10.588 --> 43:14.007
Oh, you should stop that.
This is my friend Reuben.

43:14.884 --> 43:16.009
This is Javi.

43:16.094 --> 43:18.720
